What is that crystal structure?
It is either body-centered cubic or

00:43:06.150 --> 00:43:10.760
face-centered cubic.
The two are the same in

00:43:10.760 --> 00:43:15.380
two-dimensions.
This would exhibit four-fold

00:43:15.380 --> 00:43:34.760
symmetry. This pattern exhibits
four-fold symmetry. This one.

00:43:00.000 --> 00:43:24.760
Symmetry now. Three-fold symmetry.
120. I even tried it. I rotated

