This is two-fold.
Remember this?

00:44:21.870 --> 00:44:25.620
This one is, you can see,
a 60 degree angle, but you can see

00:44:25.620 --> 00:44:29.370
this has three-fold symmetry.
This gets back to somebody who said

00:44:29.370 --> 00:44:33.120
60 degrees. You can see this
